{
  "texts": [
    "The co-share network is obtained by projecting the bipartite network onto account nodes. 3.",
    "We label a subset of account nodes in the network.",
    "These labels are derived from source credibility scores provided by a fact-checking organization, such as NewsGuardfoot_0 or Media Bias Fact Check.",
    "2 To obtain an account label, we calculate the weighted mean of all the sources they shared and then apply a threshold to this mean score, following the organization's standard for the credibility threshold. 4.",
    "Each algorithm is applied to propagate or compute credibility scores for all nodes. 5."
  ]
}